{"uuid":"recommended211207","createDate":1643487540000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"211207\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:06:21\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2022-01-30\",\"gameName\":\"The Revenge of Shinobi\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/211207\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/211207/\",\"playTime\":\"3.3\",\"updateTime\":\"2022-01-30\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"2.9\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/211207\"}","title":"评测 > The Revenge of Shinobi","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  ~&lt;超级忍&gt;世嘉MD官方ROM~\n  <br>\n  ~感觉就是89年的抖M游戏~好难好难好难~QAQ~\n </div><span class=\"bb_spoiler\"><span>！！这游戏和我同龄！！ </span></span>\n <br>\n <br>\n 玩着这游戏就感觉忍者就只有手里剑！\n <br>\n 敌人不是会飞就是隐身甚至还无敌！···怎么打啊！哎···\n <br>\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  ~游戏Boss有蜘蛛侠和蝙蝠侠和哥斯拉！！！\n  <br>\n  不过蝙蝠侠因为版权原因后来变成另外一个像蝙蝠的角色了···\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  这游戏的二段跳很难！要在一定时机按下才能按得出来！\n  <br>\n  不像现在的游戏随意按两下就能跳出来的！\n </div>首先第一下跳跃到一定高度后再按一下才会出现二段跳！有一种特殊的节奏感！\n <br>\n 不像现在的游戏随意按2下就2段跳成功···\n <br>\n <br>\n 还有各种奇怪的Boss，恶心的迷宫，更恶心的是平台跳跃~~\n <br>\n 最终Boss也是个恶心的长发鬼···为了救小姐姐我都快把手柄按废了···\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736716265\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736716265</a>\n <br>\n ~Bad End怎么能忍！我又不是忍者！必须打出Happy End~\n <br>\n ···重试了N次终于···\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736715969\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736715969</a>\n <br>\n ~终于Happy End了~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736715291\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736715291</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n 游戏一共8个关卡！\n <br>\n 剧情：\n <br>\n 犯罪集团Zeed在被乔·武藏（Jo